'''Tarifit''' (qqaren as '''Tamaziγt''' di Arif) d tantala d Tamaziɣt i ttmeslayen [[Arif|Irifiyen]] di ugafa n [[Merruk|Umerruk]]. 

Tantala Tarifit ssawalen tt 3,5 mlyun n imdanen. 

Haten imgirrden ger Tarifit d tanaliwin Timaziɣin nniḍen:

* /l/ yuɣal-d /r/, Amedya : ''ul'' -> ''ur''
* Ur nentiq ara /r/ asmi yellan qbel asekkil: ''taddart'' -> ''taddat''. Lemmer tella tiɣra mbeɛd /r/ a t-nenteq, Amedya : nenteq /r/ n ''tamara''.
* /ll/ yuɣal-d /ǧ/, Amedya : ''yelli'' -> ''yeǧǧi''.
* /lt/ yuɣal-d /č/, Amedya : ''weltma'' -> ''wečma''.
* S umata /k/ yuɣal-d /c/.
* Tikkwal, ur nenteq ara leprefix ''a-'', Amedya : ''afus'' -> ''fus''.

